        "content": "<p>fitzgen opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12670\">PR #12670</a> from <code>fitzgen:handle-oom-in-environ-wasm-func-type</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It should also not <code>#[derive(Clone)]</code> anymore, just <code>TryClone</code>, which propagates out to a bunch of other types as well.</p>\n<p>And while we are here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Rename its \"returns\" to \"results\" to match Wasmtime's public API and also the   Wasm text format.</li>\n<li>Store both its params and results in a single allocation.</li>\n<li>Shrink its size on 64-bit architectures by storing its param- and   result-GC-type counts as <code>u32</code>s rather than <code>usize</code>s.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Depends on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12669\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12669</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
